r: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"7bda9895037c83ef8076b6262d657aaafa19c221","tid":1634404,"uid":284034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:03:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8304f26248b61bbf8d1cb2d26cc66be83c74a23","tid":1634404,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:03:16.000Z","msg":"diu 正喎喂"},{"pid":"f945bc414c2910c8afa36355606bbeadafce4f5b","tid":1634404,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3705282fed3b6ab839426a686bb2f90eedc1ffb5","tid":1634404,"uid":264978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tXiKD5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtXiKD5m.jpg&h=0d7f3385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家唔好放過黨鐵，追返自己應得嘅，等佢停鐵停得咁開心.... 千祈唔好便宜咗佢。<br />\n<br />\n唔該share俾你身邊有買月票嘅朋友，我知好多住大東北嘅都有買㗎.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"仲買月票已經...唔識講<br />\n不過做啦, 加下班友行政手續都好."},{"pid":"0c6d138d73f0b2652ae5e3e8c66d789440d43202","tid":1634404,"uid":47462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:21:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a191b1a6b11701bb46417a60af2821469a7a74e","tid":1634404,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"買左既記得拎晒自己應得既野